            <p class="au-content">
                Born from the founder, Ishwarya Balabharathy’s love for the art, NatyaTaara is a dance school, based on connection and trust. Founded in September 2015 in the depths of Slough, UK today NatyaTaara has grown into a school of over 100 students  in Chennai at K. K. Nagar. At NatyaTaara, we value dance as not just another art form but as a medium of creative self-expression, empowering its students to align with their true nature. NatyaTaara’s vision is to create an environment conducive to encourage and support students who are passionate about a career in dance. We nurture this through two distinct styles - Bharathanatyam and Cinematic Freestyle (Bollywood). Each of these styles are taught through a structured syllabus. Our revered practice partnerships with the well-known Prayathnam thereby training our students to be certified learners of Bharathanatyam. Additionally, we train students pursuing BFA and MFA in Bharathanatyam. NatyaTaara also specialises in corporate shows and wedding choreographies. At NatyaTaara, we believe in welcoming our students and clients not just into an academy but into a family where they learn, grow, connect and have fun! 
